{"id":989430979,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"2 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1688832069,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"371 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/989430979/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Relocate Marbles","memory":"176.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    vector<int> relocateMarbles(vector<int>& nums, vector<int>& moveFrom, vector<int>& moveTo) {\n        // Sort the nums vector and remove duplicates\n        sort(nums.begin(), nums.end());\n\n        unordered_map<int, int> marbleMap;\n        int n = nums.size();\n        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n            marbleMap[nums[i]] = 1;\n        }\n\n        int m = moveFrom.size();\n        for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {\n            if (marbleMap.find(moveFrom[i]) != marbleMap.end()) {\n                // Marble found in the map\n                marbleMap.erase(moveFrom[i]);\n                marbleMap[moveTo[i]] = 1;\n            }\n        }\n\n        vector<int> relocatedMarbles;\n        for (auto it : marbleMap) {\n            relocatedMarbles.push_back(it.first);\n        }\n\n        sort(relocatedMarbles.begin(), relocatedMarbles.end());\n        return relocatedMarbles;\n    }\n};\n","compare_result":"","title_slug":"relocate-marbles","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
